      // unconditionally, including their head, is intentional).
      // Built once per changeDirection() call (not once per simulated hop
      // below) since none of this changes mid-simulation — the simulation
      // is a static-world look-ahead, same as it's always been for the
      // grid edges. Empty set = no hazard yet, so every trail check below
