      // itself is the blocker. If the new heading would immediately walk into
      // a grid edge (within 1 tile), pause the player instead of silently
      // swallowing the input — this prevents the frustrating "running along
      // the wall while hammering a turn key and nothing happens" UX.
      if (heading !== 4 && willPathCrash(heading)) {
